811
00:55:32.934 --> 00:55:33.968
Let's go.

812
00:55:51.484 --> 00:55:52.753
We should leave.

813
00:55:55.623 --> 00:55:57.058
Do what the fuck you want.

814
00:56:02.663 --> 00:56:03.698
Okay.

815
00:56:07.802 --> 00:56:08.970
