I am.

920
01:06:40.234 --> 01:06:42.035
But here's the thing.

921
01:06:42.069 --> 01:06:44.271
They fucking bollocksed it up.

922
01:06:44.304 --> 01:06:45.607
They didn't get
what they came for.

923
01:06:45.640 --> 01:06:48.408
They didn't get
anything. really.

924
01:06:48.442 --> 01:06:50.043
Except one over on
the rich prick

925
01:06:50.077 --> 01:06:51.445
