And you haven't even
fucking killed anyone.

930
01:07:06.393 --> 01:07:08.328
I know.

931
01:07:08.362 --> 01:07:11.566
It feels fucking good.

932
01:07:11.599 --> 01:07:13.668
And the more you do it.
the more you wonder

933
